thread.title: Gail Macleod-Jones

author: Gail Macleod-Jones
title: Gail Macleod-Jones
text:
After researching numerous companies, our club decided on Havealook to create and build our new website.
Patiently, the developers worked with our list of needs and wants to produce a website which has had a positive impact on the club's communications.
Editing the website is quick and easy, meaning that it is kept up to date with relevant information and news - a must when communicating with 800 members.
The ongoing support is just an email or telephone call away which is reassuring.
Cranebrook United SC gladly recommends Havealook for value, customer service and outstanding product.
